    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/c9d64de00679bab9e1e7698cfd6254e4.avif?t=1770024700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras_big/c9d64de00679bab9e1e7698cfd6254e4.avif?t=1770024700 width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spectral Sonata</strong> is a first-person psychological horror experience set in a grand, decaying estate. As you navigate the shifting corridors, you uncover fragments of a tragic story tied to a prodigious musician whose presence still lingers within the house. The mansion subtly rearranges itself as you progress, revealing new passages, hidden rooms, and unsettling memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/374c487023ef5ccc6958d38c03a3bc29.poster.avif?t=1770024700\" width=800 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/374c487023ef5ccc6958d38c03a3bc29.webm?t=1770024700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/374c487023ef5ccc6958d38c03a3bc29.mp4?t=1770024700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haunting melodies echo through the halls, sometimes offering guidance, other times signaling imminent danger. Piece together the past by discovering scattered notes, forgotten memories, and environmental clues. Your actions and understanding of the tragedy dictate your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you escape the mansion’s grasp, drive the spirit away, or finally set its soul free?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/e0cc9f2a3c6b2bad1fac7604598c14e9.poster.avif?t=1770024700\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/e0cc9f2a3c6b2bad1fac7604598c14e9.webm?t=1770024700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/e0cc9f2a3c6b2bad1fac7604598c14e9.mp4?t=1770024700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Tension:</strong> A slow-burn experience built on tension, unease, and anticipation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Exploration:</strong> Explore a dynamic environment where the layout shifts as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sound-Driven Gameplay:</strong> Music and ambient audio guide, warn, and shape the experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environmental Storytelling:</strong> Uncover the narrative through notes, memories, and subtle visual details.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong> The conclusion is determined by your actions and understanding of the story.</p></li></ul>",
